Brighten up your wardrobe with this feminine pair of Yalu Glam shoes from puma. Sleek, comfortable and strong with a delicate looking design, these shoes look great when teamed with shorts, mini skirts or denims and tees for a cool casual look.

Upper
Synthetic leather upper for lightweight durability
Stitch detailing and formstripes for style
Textile lining for superior comfort
puma cat appliqued on the toe box and collar
Embroidered logo on the tongue
Satin lace ups for style with a slip on design for ease of wear

Midsole
EcoOrthoLite midsole for maximum comfort, protection from impact and support

Outsole
TPU outsole with wave grooves for traction and grip
Embedded pivot point on the toe mound and heel for 180 degree movement of the foot

shoe care
Wipe surface with soft, clean, damp cloth to remove dust
Do not wash or store in direct sunlight

name: Puma Women Aurora Shoes
description:
These stylish Aurora shoes for women from puma have a friendly design and are great for urban wear. These shoes infused with their attractive low-profile design look great when teamed with jeans and a tee for a cool casual look.

Upper
Leather uppers for durability and protection
Lightly padded collar and tongue for greater comfort
Textile lining for extra comfort
Brand logo embossed on the tongue and heel
Central lace ups for a snug and customised Fit

Midsole
Eco-friendly EcoOrtholite insole gives breathability, moisture control, anti-microbial properties, and long term cushioning
Foam midsole for greater lightweight comfort

Outsole
Non-slip rubber outsole in a tyre tread pattern for greater traction
Terraced lugs for greater flexibility of the feet

shoe care
Wipe surface with soft, clean, damp cloth to remove dust
Do not store in direct sunlight
